  <summary date="2020-12-08T20:20:06Z" status="Introduced in House">Fair Access to Financial Services Act of 2020 

This bill prohibits financial institutions from discriminating on the basis of race, color, religion, national origin, or sex, including sexual orientation and gender identity. The bill also provides an aggrieved person with a private right of action for preventive relief.</summary>
